\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614234\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614234\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 06, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kvj1665702609788.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kvj1665702609788.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kvj1665702609788.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kvj1665702609788\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether the widget is transparent.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__p_d108383e1_d108384e1_d108385e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>Transparency<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__table_d12764e1_d12765e1_d12766e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__table_d12764e1_d12765e1_d12766e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__table_d12764e1_d12765e1_d12766e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kvj1665702609788__table_d12764e1_d12765e1_d12766e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n</p> (default)\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kvj1665702609788__table_d12764e1_d12765e1_d12766e1__entry__2\">Widget is displayed using the widget's background\n                     color. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kvj1665702609788__table_d12764e1_d12765e1_d12766e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kvj1665702609788__table_d12764e1_d12765e1_d12766e1__entry__2\">Widget is displayed with transparent background,\n                     so the color or image on the underlying form or entity is visible. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__section_svw_f4f_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d257474e115\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__table_d12767e1_d12768e1_d12769e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes for widgets; No for labels </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__section_ddd_h4f_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d257474e161\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__p_d108392e1_d108393e1_d108394e1\">When <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transparency</span> is\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Background Color</span> of the widget or\n            label is ignored, and the underlying color or image is displayed.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__section_xdt_34f_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d257474e179\">Edit Box</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__p_d108398e1_d108399e1_d108400e1\">When <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transparency</span> is\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, the performance may be slower because each time a user enters\n            a character or the focus changes, the window is redrawn to display the widget\n            content.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__note_v5q_k4f_1xb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> For this reason, it is best to use this property\n            only if the widget overlaps a background image. Otherwise, just rely on the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Background Color</span> property.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__p_d108401e1_d108402e1_d108403e1\">If the field value is longer than the field size\n            and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Alignment</span> is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">right</code> or\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">center</code> , the contents are left-aligned and will not be scrolled.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__section_btx_k4f_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d257474e213\">Radio Group</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__p_d108407e1_d108408e1_d108409e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transparency</span> property\n            should be set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">false</code> to ensure that the radio buttons are correctly\n            rendered as circles rather than hexagons. If <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transparency</span> is\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, they appear as hexagons.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__section_sfb_n4f_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d257474e234\">Check Box</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__p_d108425e1_d108426e1_d108427e1\">For the Check Box widget, the associated label is\n            transparent, so the background is not painted.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__section_rqy_p4f_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d257474e243\">Label</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__p_d108431e1_d108432e1_d108433e1\">For labels, setting\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">Transparency=True</code> is useful when a label is on top of an image or is\n            part of a line frame.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__p_d108434e1_d108435e1_d108436e1\">In character mode (CHUI), this property has no\n            effect. To have the label appear transparent, set the background color of the label to\n            the background color of the parent widget or entity.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__section_gcr_kpf_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d257474e258\">Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__p_d108440e1_d108441e1_d108442e1\">This property can be set in ProcScript for widgets,\n            but not for labels.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__section_x4b_mpf_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d257474e267\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__ul_v4d_npf_1xb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__li_d42326e1_d42327e1_d42328e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fxi1688449052174.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fxi1688449052174.html\" title=\"The ucheckbox widget enables the user to set a Boolean value in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called CheckBox, which is mapped to ucheckbox.\">ucheckbox (CheckBox)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__li_d42329e1_d42330e1_d42331e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrc1665702631553.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" title=\"The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.\">CommandButton</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__li_d42332e1_d42333e1_d42334e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"klb1688454363706.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/klb1688454363706.html\" title=\"Default logical widget for entering and displaying data in a field in a Form or Report.\">EditBox</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__li_d42335e1_d42336e1_d42337e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hta1665703126401.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hta1665703126401.html\" title=\"The uhyperlink widget is a display-only widget that acts like a hyperlink in a web page. It activates a command when the user clicks it. It can only be used in form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called Hyperlink, which is mapped to uhyperlink.\">uhyperlink (Hyperlink)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__li_d42338e1_d42339e1_d42340e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yye1665702650577.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yye1665702650577.html\" title=\"The uradiogroup widget displays a set of mutually exclusive choices as a group of radio buttons. Uniface provides a logical widget called RadioGroup, which is mapped to uradiogroup.\">uradiogroup (RadioGroup)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__li_d42341e1_d42342e1_d42343e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxc1665703126500.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxc1665703126500.html\" title=\"The upicture widget is used to displays the contents of an Image field. Uniface provides a logical widget called Picture, which is mapped to upicture.\">upicture (Picture)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kvj1665702609788__li_d42344e1_d42345e1_d42346e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ngv1688454370143.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ngv1688454370143.html\" title=\"A label displays text on a component, such as the name of an associated field or an instruction to the user.\">Label</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614234\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614234\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Transparency Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 06, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Determines whether the widget is transparent. \" Transparency = False | True \" Value Description False (default) Widget is displayed using the widget's background color. True Widget is displayed with transparent background, so the color or image on the underlying form or entity is visible. Usage Dynamic? Yes for widgets; No for labels Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description When Transparency is True , the Background Color of the widget or label is ignored, and the underlying color or image is displayed. Edit Box When Transparency is True , the performance may be slower because each time a user enters a character or the focus changes, the window is redrawn to display the widget content. Note: For this reason, it is best to use this property only if the widget overlaps a background image. Otherwise, just rely on the Background Color property. If the field value is longer than the field size and Alignment is set to right or center , the contents are left-aligned and will not be scrolled. Radio Group The Transparency property should be set to false to ensure that the radio buttons are correctly rendered as circles rather than hexagons. If Transparency is True , they appear as hexagons. Check Box For the Check Box widget, the associated label is transparent, so the background is not painted. Label For labels, setting Transparency=True is useful when a label is on top of an image or is part of a line frame. In character mode (CHUI), this property has no effect. To have the label appear transparent, set the background color of the label to the background color of the parent widget or entity. Setting in ProcScript This property can be set in ProcScript for widgets, but not for labels. Applies To ucheckbox (CheckBox) CommandButton EditBox uhyperlink (Hyperlink) uradiogroup (RadioGroup) upicture (Picture) Label Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}